# === Monorepo root — only track README + the two app folders ===
# Ignore everything at the monorepo root by default...
/*

# ...then re-include the essentials
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/FE-BikeStore-main/
!/LightWeightBikeStore-main/

# === Global safety net (applies inside the two subfolders too) ===
# Each subfolder has its own .gitignore, but we double up on the most
# sensitive / heavy items so a missing pattern can't leak them.

# Secrets
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Python
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/env/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd

# Node / Vite
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/

# IDE / OS
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
*.code-workspace
